title: Cheesy Sweetcorn and Potato Soup
ingredients: ['310g peeled and diced potatoes', '65g diced carrots', '60g diced celery', '4 tablespoons chopped onion', '1 teaspoon salt', '50g butter', '475ml milk', '4 tablespoons plain flour', '2 1/2 (340g) tins sweetcorn, drained', '280g grated Cheddar cheese']
